# Project Health — <%= appName %>

Enterprise project analysis for architecture, security, dependencies, testing, documentation, deployment readiness, and performance risks.

## CLI

```bash
my doctor
my doctor setup
my doctor --skip-audit
```

## Output

`project-health-report.md`

## Layout

```
src/project-health/
  analyzers/
  reports/
tests/project-health/
PROJECT_HEALTH.md
project-health-report.md
```

## Usage

```ts
import { registerProjectHealth } from './src/project-health/index.js';

const health = registerProjectHealth();
const report = health.analyze({
  projectName: '<%= appName %>',
  architectureStyle: 'modular-monolith',
  features: { security: true },
  existingPaths: ['src/security', 'README.md'],
});
console.log(health.render(report));
```
